\newlabel{tab:hard}{{5}{9}{\yatcc {}-Hard leaderboard (top 8 of 18). Scores drop significantly compared to \yatcc {}---the best model achieves only PL=94.5 on Hard vs.\ PL=99.3 on \yatcc {}.\relax }{table.caption.7}{}}
